{"tid":962295,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟杜琪峰影響咗幾多巨星","createTime":"2018-12-30T17:55:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-27T14:22:25.000Z","uid":115169,"like":98,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"c1d11f054bf173439b4275966d47374fa77a4277","tid":962295,"uid":115169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T17:55:36.000Z","msg":"暗戰令劉德華攞金像獎最佳男主角<br />\n黑社會令張家輝由化骨龍發展到一種戲路<br />\n古天樂因為杜琪峰嘅電影變得更加多人認識<br />\n槍火拍都振宇耀揚秋生同林雪超有型，之後仲有放逐<br />\n連劉青雲，梁朝偉同周星馳都係佢嘅電影有一個好大嘅發揮<br />\n<br />\n杜琪峰堪稱香港影壇教父真係當之無愧<br />\n（可惜香港最好戲嘅張國榮未同佢合作過，唔係一定變成一個佳話）"},{"pid":"e234f973e128b58a37e74825438ce07105172721","tid":962295,"uid":27416,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T17:58:40.000Z","msg":"黃浩然"},{"pid":"54f994cea72b6bc10536c88f7bb2f20286f5e9c8","tid":962295,"uid":51920,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T18:00:17.000Z","msg":"漏左鄭臭四"},{"pid":"af3010f9a9316b259ca3b9d7117de9f3d4dcc47a","tid":962295,"uid":27530,"like":3,"dislike":78,"score":-75,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T18:01:08.000Z","msg":"無杜琪峰都年年會有金像獎最佳男主角，我知你想講啲野，但你篇野係無邏輯可言，試下重寫。"},{"pid":"a0a20f5951dff77767e7b4d4392f388d768ef372","tid":962295,"uid":115169,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"quote":{"pid":"af3010f9a9316b259ca3b9d7117de9f3d4dcc47a","tid":962295,"uid":27530,"like":3,"dislike":78,"score":-75,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T18:01:08.000Z","msg":"無杜琪峰都年年會有金像獎最佳男主角，我知你想講啲野，但你篇野係無邏輯可言，試下重寫。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T18:02:02.000Z","msg":"做咩姐你"},{"pid":"3945707832a2ac2aebc03576b52228dd30c4520c","tid":962295,"uid":68896,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T18:05:10.000Z","msg":"如果拍張國榮<br />\n<br />\n我覺得會似槍王既張國榮<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21295515a6f3999f769398404e8a126a576c2130","tid":962295,"uid":27530,"like":4,"dislike":65,"score":-61,"quote":{"pid":"a0a20f5951dff77767e7b4d4392f388d768ef372","tid":962295,"uid":115169,"like":37,"dislike":1